{"word":"G889 - ἀχρειόω - achreióō - akh-ri-o'-o - Become unprofitable","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἀχρειόω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">achreióō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">akh-ri-o'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Become unprofitable</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - கெட்டுப்போ"},{"paragraph":"to make useless, render unserviceable"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G888 - ἀχρεῖος - achreîos - akh-ri'-os/888\">G888</a>; to <i>render useless</i>, that is, <i>spoil:</i> - become unprofitable.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}